summary: En Estados Unidos, el Día de San Patricio se celebra el 17 de marzo para honrar la herencia irlandesa. En ciudades como Nueva York, Chicago y Boston, se llevan a cabo grandes desfiles, donde la gente viste de verde y disfruta de música y bailes irlandeses. Miami, Washington D.C. y otras ciudades del DMV también organizan festividades que incluyen actividades para familias, música en vivo y cierres de calles para los desfiles. Además, hay datos curiosos sobre el Día de San Patricio que se destacan en los artículos, como su origen irlandés, el uso del trébol como símbolo, y la tradición de beber cerveza verde.

name: St patty's Day
summary: St. Patrick's Day, also known as the Feast of Saint Patrick, commemorates the patron saint of Ireland on March 17th. The correct nickname for the holiday is "St. Paddy's Day," as the nickname "St. Patty's Day" is a common misnomer. Various cities and regions are hosting events to celebrate, including parades, festive gatherings, and cultural events. From Boston to Savannah, Des Moines to Asheville, Houston to South Carolina, and the Tri-Cities, people are planning festivities to mark the occasion. Whether you prefer to gather for parades or seek alternative ways to celebrate, there are many opportunities to embrace Irish culture and the spirit of St. Patrick's Day.

name: L.A. Marathon 2024
summary: The 2024 LA Marathon will take place on March 17th and is expected to be the largest in history with over 40,000 participants. The marathon course will be the same as in previous years, starting at Dodger Stadium and finishing at the Santa Monica Pier. Several roads and freeway ramps will be closed on Sunday, March 17th, to accommodate the marathon. Kenyan runners dominated the 2024 LA Marathon, with Dominic Ngeno and Stacy Ndiwa taking first place in the men's and women's races, respectively.

name: St. Patrick's Day
summary: St. Patrick's Day is a globally celebrated event with deep-rooted history and traditions. From the iconic symbol of four-leaf clovers to the solemn processions in Savannah, this holiday holds cultural significance. While parades draw large crowds in cities like Huntsville, Manhattan, and Boston, there are unique and alternative ways to commemorate St. Patrick's Day. Surprising facts about the holiday include the lesser-known fact that Ireland's patron saint is not the only one celebrated on this day. Additionally, the prevalence of green attire during the festivities stems from its association with the Emerald Isle and the shamrock, a symbol of the Holy Trinity.

name: NC State Basketball
summary: NC State's men's basketball team has had a remarkable run in the ACC Tournament, defying expectations to reach the championship game. After defeating Louisville in the first round, they upset No. 4 North Carolina in the semifinals to secure an automatic bid to the NCAA Tournament. In the championship game, they faced rival UNC again and pulled off another upset victory, completing an improbable Cinderella run. This historic triumph marks the first ACC Tournament title for NC State since 1989 and is a testament to the team's determination and resilience.

name: Lakers
summary: The Lakers and Warriors recently faced off, with the Warriors emerging victorious with a 128-121 score despite LeBron James's impressive 40 points. D'Angelo Russell's strong performance has solidified his place in the Lakers' future, potentially hindering Trae Young's chances of joining the team. Former teammate and top pick Brandon Ingram discusses how James' presence on the court enhances his own game. The game's finale was marred by an unusual incident where the arena announcer mistakenly announced the shot clock, prompting criticism. Austin Reaves expresses confidence in the Lakers' current standing as one of the best teams in the NBA. Despite their recent loss to the Warriors, the Lakers are exploring a new sports drink partnership and seeking guidance from LeBron James to improve their performance.
